== English ==
=== Etymology ===
British television show [[w:Blue Peter|Blue Peter]] invented the term due to its policy against using commercial terms on-air. The commercial term for it was [[Fablon]].
=== Noun ===
'''[[sticky]]-[[backed]] [[plastic]]'''
# (''UK'') large sheet of [[thin]], [[soft]], [[colour]]ed plastic that is sticky on one side
==== Synonyms ====
* (''US'') [[contact paper]]